EN: I can feel the warmth in my nostrils as I breathe in the cold air.

ZH: 她用手指轻轻拭去鼻翼上的泪水。
EN: She gently wipes away the tears from her nostrils with her fingers.

ZH: 这个动作会导致鼻翼肿胀。
EN: This action can cause nasal inflammation.

ZH: 在过敏季节，我的鼻翼经常肿胀。
EN: During allergy season, my nostrils often swell.

ZH: 需要经常清洁鼻翼，以防止感染。
EN: It is important to clean the nostrils regularly to prevent infection.

